Exiv2Net
********

Welcome to Exiv2Net, a .NET wrapper for the Exiv2 C++ library. The 
homepage of Exiv2 is:

    http://www.exiv2.org/

The homepage of Exiv2Net is:

    http://code.google.com/p/exiv2net/

Building and Installing
=======================

Use Microsoft Visual Studio 2008 to build Exiv2Net. Open

    exiv2net/exiv2net.sln
    
and select "Build -> Build Solution" to build everything.
 
Dependencies
============

All dependencies to build Exiv2Net are available in the SVN repository.
The Exiv2 source code is added as an SVN external.

The only dependency which is not included in the SVN repository is
NUnit, which you need to run the unit tests in exiv2net/exiv2netut.
NUnit is available at:

    http://www.nunit.org/index.php

